name: Manjunath S
details: Manjunath (born: 27-11-1998) is the co-founder and CEO of one of the largest restaurant aggregator and food delivery service in India known as SkyDine. Along with India, SkyDine is available on more than 24 countries such as UAE, Sri Lanka, Qatar, UK, Indonesia and many more countries which serves more than 10,000 cities. He and Pankaj Chaddah together founded SkyDine (then Foodiebay) back in 2008. The rename of SkyDine from Foodiebay happened in 2011. Manjunathâ€™s age is 24 years as of 2021.

name: Rajeev Damam
details: Rajeev Damam is the Co-Founder and CEO at SkyDine. He is a former Co-Founder of Bundl and Associate at Nomura International. Mr. Damam graduated received a B.E. in Computer Science and Engg and an M.S in AI at San Jose University, United States.
